《'''玻璃之城電影原聲大碟'''》（{{lang-en|''City of Glass: Original Soundtrack''}}）是[[香港電影|香港電影]]《[[玻璃之城|玻璃之城]]》的[[原聲帶|原聲帶]]，於1998年10月14日由[[索尼音樂娛樂_(香港)|新力唱片]]首次發行，專輯曾經登上香港大型連鎖唱片店[[HMV|HMV]]的中文唱片銷量榜冠軍，截至1998年10月底錄得超過二萬五千張銷量<ref name="銷量">{{cite news |language = zh | url = https://i.imgur.com/ZlkgUMq.jpg |title = 電影原聲碟銷量創紀錄 黎明打破不賣宿命|publisher = 報章 | date = 1998-10-27 |accessdate = 2022-03-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210614073643/https://i.imgur.com/ZlkgUMq.jpg|archive-date = 2021-06-14|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

==製作與發行==
《玻璃之城電影原聲大碟》是配合電影《玻璃之城》而推出的專輯，收錄黎明主唱的粵語、國語及英文各一首，以及電影內的其他音樂<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.discogs.com/Various-City-Of-Glass-Soundtrack/release/8819036 |title = Various－City Of Glass－Soundtrack |date = 1998 |publisher = Discogs |language = en |accessdate = 2022-03-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017071616/https://www.discogs.com/Various-City-Of-Glass-Soundtrack/release/8819036|archive-date = 2020-10-17|dead-url = no}}</ref>，唱片公司擇定於1998年10月14日下午1時開售<ref>{{cite news |language = zh | url = https://i.imgur.com/q9Ed6vr.jpg |title = 黎明舒淇激吻 |publisher = 東方日報 |pages = C12 | date = 1998-10-10 |accessdate = 2022-03-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210614073438/https://i.imgur.com/q9Ed6vr.jpg|archive-date = 2021-06-14|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，定價為港幣85元，隨碟附送電影優惠券、劇照名信片、電影拉頁圖輯及VCD，VCD收錄了4首歌曲的音樂短片及卡拉OK版本，音樂短片的製作費約港幣一百多萬元，包括電腦加工及向電影公司購買電影片段加插在音樂短片中<ref>{{cite news |language = zh | url = https://i.imgur.com/uZ45MR0.jpg |title = 黎明的新碟中送出拉頁圖輯 |publisher = 明報 | date = 1998-10-10 |accessdate = 2022-03-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210614073250/https://i.imgur.com/uZ45MR0.jpg|archive-date = 2021-06-14|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。主題曲〈今生不再〉的音樂短片由黎明和[[舒淇|舒淇]]主演<ref>{{cite news |language = zh | url = http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20000304/C16-01.html |title = 情到濃時懶理閒言 黎明舒淇情侶檔拍MTV |publisher = 蘋果日報 |pages = C16 | date = 2000-03-04 |accessdate =2021-06-28|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210628023359/http://newsbot.lib.cuhk.edu.hk/news/apple/20000304/C16-01.html|archive-date = 2021-06-28|dead-url = no}}</ref>，共有三個版本，包括香港粵語、國語及中國內地版本，中國內地版本刪去學生抗議鏡頭，以配合當地市場，這首歌由[[李炳文_(新加坡)|李迪文]]作曲、[[林夕|林夕]]填詞、黎明主唱，〈今生不再〉的「今生」，除了指一對戀人的今生，也解讀為香港的今生，通過歌詞表達出對逝去愛情的感慨，同時暗中寄寓香港昔日繁榮盛世「今生不再」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/05/02/132581/ |title = 黎明 許港生 閱讀《玻璃之城》|author = 青木原 |date = 2016-05-02 |publisher = 輔仁文誌 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190929044810/https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/05/02/132581/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E3%80%81%E8%A8%B1%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%9F%E3%80%81%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80%E3%80%8A%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E4%B9%8B%E5%9F%8E%E3%80%8B|archive-date = 2019-09-29|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.now.com/home/life/player?newsId=156922 |title =〈Glocal Pop〉《今生不再》|author = 沈旭暉 |date = 2015-11-06 |publisher = Now新聞 |language = zh |accessdate =2020-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201017080119/https://news.now.com/home/life/player?newsId=156922|archive-date = 2020-10-17|dead-url = no}}</ref>。歌曲〈Try to Remember〉是黎明首次灌錄的英文歌，這是一首1960年代的舊曲，為配合電影劇情而重新演繹<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/IvDOHu3.jpg |title = 黎明無懼寶記出碟對撼 |date = 1998 |publisher = 報章 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-03-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220318235021/https://i.imgur.com/IvDOHu3.jpg|archive-date = 2022-03-19|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

